{"tid":474459,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［港產禁片］有冇巴絲睇過《第一類型危險》？（內有觀後感）","createTime":"2017-11-20T07:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T23:24:28.000Z","uid":27151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"875e80808e09407ddc6a991332ed8a9f6ad2c360","tid":474459,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"尋晚上網搵到呢套被喻為香港經典cult片、新浪潮重要之作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年套戲仲比港英政府bam咗（驚搞到再有六七暴動），搞到要cut咗放炸彈情節同改戲名先有得公映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係估唔到30幾年前嘅徐克都曾經係個激進憤青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_JXBobRKYXEQ/SXhKZybjH7I/AAAAAAAACio/SoCUZeYbcUY/s320/1121347e309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F_JXBobRKYXEQ%2FSXhKZybjH7I%2FAAAAAAAACio%2FSoCUZeYbcUY%2Fs320%2F1121347e309.jpg&h=e4053aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下面有少量劇透</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n觀後感：成套戲由頭到尾嘅格調都相當黑暗，而劇情同鏡頭運用都非常大膽，影像凌厲兼張力十足。由其向前面已經有虐待動物嘅鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女真係好撚恐怖<img src=\"http://gb.cri.cn/mmsource/images/2011/12/21/47/2421430545873452419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgb.cri.cn%2Fmmsource%2Fimages%2F2011%2F12%2F21%2F47%2F2421430545873452419.jpg&h=be9f0533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n套戲充斥住大量反社會、反殖民嘅意識，以及對當時政局嘅預視、社會環境嘅批判，從中滲透出年青人對未來強烈嘅虛無感、壓抑感、無力感。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/040033_d019207978c6874defc04a478c41d16d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F040033_d019207978c6874defc04a478c41d16d.jpg&h=ea8e2819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一切無從發洩嘅躁動不安結果扭曲成瘋狂嘅反社會行為，車保羅笑住狂掃和合石果幕真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劇情一路引領住佢地走向絕路，都算係一套青春殘酷物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/033321_c25b6e18effd6efa78e63021a86713d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F033321_c25b6e18effd6efa78e63021a86713d6.jpg&h=ee1e7036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反觀今日，不變嘅係我地呢代廢青𠄘接咗上一代班死衰仔果份無力感同躁動，對未來亦都依然一片迷茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但當年啲死衰仔話唔定今日都變哂做欺壓番下一代嘅廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連導演徐克都一早去咗鄰國拍商業片，悲哀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://www.morbidofest.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/pearlmirror.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.morbidofest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fpearlmirror.png&h=f3d41092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但不得不佩服佢一早就預視咗咁嘅境況，都借套戲去令社會反思點解每個時代都會出現「暴力」嘅年青人（片尾有六七暴動嘅相），係人性本惡還是社會同當權者嘅錯？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/035459_5df222c7cdcb133a84e40cb9f822dc07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F035459_5df222c7cdcb133a84e40cb9f822dc07.jpg&h=cb4d6581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋首主題曲好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係搵番區瑞強唱，歌詞match番哂佢角色嘅心聲，有陣時成長不過是個悲劇的開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N6JNKPmWyHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN6JNKPmWyHo&d=K0mr2195hrbrTEs%2BuxJlBjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=78e3df49\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N6JNKPmWyHo</a><br />\n美麗在延續　不會驟變　無奈前事漸遠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲討論下呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd487a00db4c9827c008c963f8d7a