論香港定外國都係。前排睇完另一套同期嘅cult片《打蛇》，d大特寫真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/215245_f4f73d6f921880432ee1e54f7ae82fa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F215245_f4f73d6f921880432ee1e54f7ae82fa8.jpg&h=11a89142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b66c52663176cb09784599fe7113be3a3d0089dc","tid":474459,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a86f6cc737a6849c534d8bc5616327ee23cd36","tid":474459,"uid":119405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"係咪叫我"},{"pid":"094a02c218ff4cc6d17bd9ef83476f8b71dca0d6","tid":474459,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"上年電影資料館再探新浪潮有放過 不過係渣大膽車版 都係無咗戲院放炸彈"},{"pid":"4411bc14b0e893cadab29e85c98e6c1fbb0022bc","tid":474459,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"推介烈火青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affd1bd5e61a906f313d189fd647c31a99b7ae5f","tid":474459,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f943889a7cf473290798c86dc8d77cb0db8f0b1c","tid":474459,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前七八十年代啲戲真係好激</blockquote><br />\nAgger, 唔知點解以前個年代d電影尺度反而仲大膽過而家，無論香港定外國都係。前排睇完另一套同期嘅cult片《打蛇》，d大特寫真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/215245_f4f73d6f921880432ee1e54f7ae82fa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ese